  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Four more Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bseek refuge in Dhanushkodi",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the severe economic downturn in the country, Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bare fleeing into Tamil Nadu via the Danuskodi Sea due to high prices of food and essential commodities and shortages of essential commodities.",
        "Dominic, 42, of Vavuniya district, his wife Sudarshani, 24, three members of the same family as his six-year-old son and Mahendran, 50, of Kilinochchi, set off in a piper boat at around 05.00 this morning. Went down the sand dune.",
        "The Rameswaram Marine Police went to the boat and rescued the Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200band took them to the Mandapam Marine Police Station based on the information provided by the fishermen who were fishing in the area about the Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bwho were trapped in the sand for about 4 hours.",
        "It is noteworthy that 96 Sri Lankan Tamils \u200b\u200bhave come to Tamil Nadu as refugees from March 22 to date due to the economic crisis in Sri Lanka."
      ],
